author: COMSOL
description: This example studies the heat conduction in a building structure separating two floors from the external environment. The structure is made of four materials with different thermal conductivities. The temperature distribution and the heat flux through the structure are compared with published data. This example corresponds to CaseÂ 3 in the European standard EN ISO 10211:2017 for thermal bridges in building constructions.
